title: 05/31/21 DPS Hour 1 Michael Lee
itunes:title: 05/31/21 DPS Hour 1 Michael Lee
description:
Doug Gottlieb and Rob Parker, in for Dan Patrick, react to the Lakers falling into huge trouble after Anthony Davis gets injured. Doug tells you the biggest mistake the Mavericks made that allowed the Clippers to get back into the series. Michael Lee of the Washington Post joins the guys to react to the Clippers, Anthony Davis, Kyrie Irving, and the Bucks. Plus, should Naomi Osaka face disqualification for avoiding the media at the French Open?
